Package: fastqnsn
Type: Package
Title: Fast and Optimized Qn and Sn Robust Scale Estimators
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Dennis Alexis Valin", "Dittrich",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davd@economicscience.net",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4438-8276"))
Description: High-performance, multi-threaded implementation of Rousseeuw-Croux
    Qn and Sn robust scale estimators. Re-engineered utilizing C++ arena memory
    allocation, Floyd-Rivest subset selection, cache-aware algorithm dispatch, and
    explicit 64-bit boundaries to resolve legacy integer overflows. Safely calculates
    exact scales on massive Big Data sequences up to N=10^8 on standard architectures
    while delivering 2x to 14x real-world speedup over robustbase across all sample
    sizes from N=10 to N=10^6.
